    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game you click to earn skins to trade with and to collect. You receive a drop every 30 minutes, up to 4 a day. There is a short collection of developer-created skins, with an in-game workshop up-loader for the community to create their own skins for the Steam market.  You can also get achievements for playing! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop rates (not all rarities in-game yet):<br><strong>Common</strong>: ~55.8%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Uncommon</strong>: ~33.48%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rare</strong>: ~6.7%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Epic</strong>: ~2.23%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exotic</strong>: ~1.12%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Legendary</strong>: ~0.54%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mythical</strong>: ~0.14%</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Divine</strong>: ~0.02%</p>",
